    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Zoos designed for the education and enjoyment of children and young adults, often including a petting zoo, animal shows, and exhibits of baby animals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
